          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I have built apps the traditional way. Weeks of planning, coding, debugging, deploying. Then I tried ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Emergent",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
