      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Every company has that one spreadsheet someone maintains manually. Emergent can turn that spreadsheet into a polished internal tool with user roles, filters, and data visualization. I have seen teams replace clunky Google Sheets workflows with slick web apps built in an afternoon.",
            "marks": []
          }
