      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Got a startup idea? Validate it fast. Instead of spending $15,000 on an agency, describe your product to Emergent, get a working MVP, and test it with real users this week. The speed advantage is enormous.",
