        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you are a freelancer or agency, Emergent lets you show clients a working prototype in hours instead of days. Close deals faster. Impress stakeholders. Move on to the next project sooner.",
