        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The platform supports PostgreSQL and other databases natively. Define your data models in plain English, and Emergent generates the schema, migrations, and CRUD operations automatically.",
