        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Teams can now work on the same project. Share your app description, iterate together, and deploy from a shared workspace. This is a game-changer for remote teams building internal tools.",
